# 赛博祭祖 · Cyber Ancestor Worship

A modern take on traditional Qingming Festival ancestor worship, implemented as an interactive web game.

## Project Structure

- Entry Point: [index.html](mdc:index.html) and [src/main.js](mdc:src/main.js)
- Core Components:
  - Views: [src/views/](mdc:src/views) - Main page components
  - Components: [src/components/](mdc:src/components) - Reusable UI components
  - Stores: [src/stores/](mdc:src/stores) - Pinia state management
  - Router: [src/router/](mdc:src/router) - Vue Router configuration
  - Assets: [public/assets/](mdc:public/assets) - Static resources

## Key Features

1. User Identity System
   - UUID-based guest login
   - Local storage for user preferences
   - Activity level tracking

2. Ancestor Generation
   - Personality types: Philosopher, Gossip Auntie, Livestream Host, Petty God
   - Dynamic trait generation
   - Evolution stages: Initial → Familiar → Intimate → Awakened

3. Interaction System
   - Offerings: Incense, Flowers, Kowtow
   - Emotion feedback
   - Cooldown mechanism
   - Affection level progression

4. Quote System
   - Daily quotes generation
   - Favorites collection
   - Context-aware responses

5. Mini-games
   - Ancestor's Teaching Translation Quiz
   - Soul Red Packet Rewards

6. Share System
   - Multiple templates
   - Image generation
   - Social media integration

## Tech Stack

- Vue 3 + Vite
- Element Plus UI
- Pinia State Management
- Vue Router
- HTML2Canvas
